				\begin{document}$${\varphi }^{M-I-M}$$\end{document} on all directions also as a local distortion effect on the octahedrals.

Our unit cell volume results increasing as VMASiI3<VMAGeI3<VMASnI3<VMAPbI3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
